The device is excellent, though its compact size makes it appear quite small, yet it is very convenient to use. The camera quality is outstanding, making it ideal for videography and creating reels. While the AI features and battery life could be improved, and the device seems to heat up consistently, which is a common issue with Samsung mobile devices. However, the other aspects of its performance, including sound quality, are top-notch.READ MORE
